description:
Ryan is a 24 year old..
He's in excellent shape and says he spends a lot of time in the gym on the base every day. It sure has paid off. When one of our model scouts first found him, they were certain he'd be a perfect addition to our elite Next Door Male crew. They were right. And now we're proud to be able to share Ryan with all of you.
Watch Ryan in three scenes. First in the living room, then the bathroom, and finally in the bedroom where he works himself up for a terrific finale.
title: Ryan
